Revision history for browser

0.05 2026-04-22
 - add `--ask` and `--askme` to browser.get for visible interactive takeover
 - wait for terminal confirmation before capturing the final page payload after captcha or login work
 - update tests and docs for interactive ask-mode

0.04 2026-04-22
 - add `content_type`, `body_text`, and `is_captcha` to browser responses
 - detect obvious CAPTCHA or bot-check pages in browser.get and browser.post payloads
 - update tests and docs for the richer response payload

0.03 2026-04-22
 - make browser.get return the rendered HTML body alongside URL, status, and title metadata
 - update tests and docs to match the browser.get payload contract

0.02 2026-04-21
 - add package.json for DD-managed Node dependency installation
 - align browser runtime bootstrap with DD package.json install behavior under $HOME
 - update tests and docs for the package.json dependency gate

0.01 2026-04-21
 - bootstrap the browser skill with Playwright-backed GET and POST CLI commands
 - add dependency files for nodejs and the Playwright Perl module
 - add Docker-tested coverage, documentation, and ticket records
